## Limitations
The findings are based on available reports and legal documents, which may not capture all dimensions of the issue. Additionally, ongoing legal proceedings and policy changes could alter the current landscape, and some sources may have inherent biases. Further research and updated data would be necessary for a more comprehensive understanding.